<div id="txtcont" class="span9" style="position: relative;">
    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='222:249'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-1a' );" name="028-1a" class="pb">[028-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='249:266'>禮記要義卷第二十九　問喪至深衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='266:275'>　一𥘉喪之節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='275:295'>親始死鷄斯徒跣扱上祍交手哭惻怛之心痛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='295:315'>疾之意傷腎乾肝焦肺水漿不入口三日不舉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='315:335'>火故鄰里爲之麋粥以飲食之注云親父母也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='335:355'>鷄斯當爲䈂纚聲之誤也親始死去冠二日乃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='355:375'>去䈂纚括髮也今時始喪者邪巾貊頭䈂纚之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='375:395'>存象也徒猶空也上祍深衣之裳前五藏者腎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='395:415'>在下肝在中肺在上舉三者之焦傷而心脾在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='415:442'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-1b' );" name="028-1b" class="pb">[028-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='442:455'>其中矣五家爲鄰五鄰爲里</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='455:469'>　二袒踊爵踊送形迎精之節</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='469:489'>悲哀志懣氣盛故袒而踊之所以動體安心下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='489:509'>氣也婦人不宜袒故發胸擊心爵踊殷殷田田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='509:529'>如壞墻然悲哀痛疾之至也故曰辟踊哭泣哀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='529:549'>以送之送形而徃迎精而反注云故袒而踊之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='549:569'>言聖人制法故使人然也爵踊足不絶地辟拊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='569:589'>心也哀以送之謂葬時也迎其精神而反謂反</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='589:598'>哭及日中而虞也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='598:625'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-2a' );" name="028-2a" class="pb">[028-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='625:639'>　三冠者不肉袒肉袒則著免</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='639:659'>或問曰冠者不肉袒何也曰冠至尊也不居肉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='659:679'>袒之體也故爲之免以代之也注云怪冠衣之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='679:699'>相爲也言身無飾者不敢冠冠爲䙝尊服肉袒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='699:712'>則著免免狀如冠而廣一寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='712:724'>　四童子當室則杖而免</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='724:744'>或問曰免者以何爲也曰不冠者之所服也禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='744:764'>曰童子不緦唯當室緦緦者其免也當室則免</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='764:784'>而杖矣注云怪本所爲施也不冠者猶未冠也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='784:811'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-2b' );" name="028-2b" class="pb">[028-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='811:831'>當室謂無父兄而主家者也童子不杖不杖者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='831:851'>不免當室則杖而免免冠之細別以次成人也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='851:865'>緦者其免也言免乃有緦服也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='865:881'>　五三秊之喪旣練期旣葬差相似</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='881:901'>三年之喪旣練矣有期之喪旣葬矣則帶其故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='901:921'>葛帶絰期之絰服其功衰有大功之喪亦如之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='921:942'>小功無變也注云帶其故葛帶者三年旣練期旣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='942:962'>葬差相似也絰期之葛絰三年旣練首絰除矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='962:982'>爲父旣練衰七升母旣葬衰八升凡齊衰旣葬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='982:1009'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-3a' );" name="028-3a" class="pb">[028-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1009:1029'>衰或八升或九升服其功衰服麤衰大功之麻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1029:1049'>變三年之練葛期旣葬之葛帶小於練之葛帶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1049:1069'>又當有絰亦反服其故葛帶絰期之絰差之宜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1069:1089'>也此雖變麻服葛大小同耳亦服其功衰凡三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1089:1109'>年之喪旣練始遭齊衰大功之䘮絰帶皆麻無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1109:1126'>所變於大功齊斬之服不用輕累重也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1126:1141'>　六君之母非夫人則羣臣無服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1141:1161'>君之母非夫人則羣臣無服唯近臣及僕驂乗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1161:1181'>從服唯君所服服也注云妾先君所不服也禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1181:1208'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-3b' );" name="028-3b" class="pb">[028-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1208:1228'>庶子爲後爲其母緦言唯君所服伸君也春秋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1228:1248'>之義有以小君服之者時若小君在則益不可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1248:1268'>正義曰妾先君所不服也天子諸侯爲妾無服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1268:1288'>唯大夫爲貴妾服緦故知妾先君所不服云禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1288:1308'>庶子爲後其母緦者案喪服緦麻章云庶子爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1308:1328'>父後者爲其母是也云言唯君所服伸君也者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1328:1348'>若其不爲後則爲母無服故喪服記云公子爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1348:1368'>其母練冠麻衣縓縁今以爲君得著緦麻服是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1368:1388'>伸君之尊也君旣服緦是近臣得從君服也此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1388:1415'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-4a' );" name="028-4a" class="pb">[028-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1415:1435'>謂禮之正法云春秋之義有以小君服之者鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1435:1455'>旣以正禮言之又引春秋之時不依正禮者有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1455:1475'>以爲小君之服服其妾母者是文公四年夫人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1475:1495'>風氏薨是僖公之母成風也又昭十一年夫人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1495:1515'>歸氏薨是昭公之母齊歸也皆亂丗之法非正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1515:1535'>禮也案異義云妾子立爲君得尊其母立以爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1535:1555'>夫人否今春秋公羊旣說妾子立爲君母得稱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1555:1575'>夫人故上堂稱妾屈於適也下堂稱夫人尊於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1575:1595'>國也云子不得爵命父妾子爲君得爵命其母</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1595:1622'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-4b' );" name="028-4b" class="pb">[028-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1622:1642'>者以妾在奉授於尊者有所因縁故也榖梁傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1642:1662'>曰魯僖公立妾母成風爲夫人是子爵於母以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1662:1682'>妾爲妻非禮也故春秋左氏說成風妾得立爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1682:1702'>夫人母以子貴禮也許君謹案舜爲天子瞽瞍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1702:1722'>爲士起於士庶者子不得爵父母也至於魯僖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1722:1742'>公得尊母成風爲小君經無譏文從公羊左氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1742:1762'>之說鄭則從榖梁之說故異義駮云父爲長子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1762:1782'>三年爲衆子期明無二適也女君卒繼攝其事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1782:1802'>耳不得復立爲夫人如鄭駮之言則此云春秋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1802:1829'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-5a' );" name="028-5a" class="pb">[028-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1829:1849'>小君服之者是灼然非禮也云時若小君在則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1849:1869'>益不可者其小君無而以夫人服之巳爲不可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1869:1887'>今小君旣在而以夫人服妾母彌益不可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1887:1904'><span class='krp-note'>十/一</span>外宗之女有三内宗有二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1904:1924'>熊氏云凡外宗有三案周禮外宗之女有爵通</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1924:1944'>卿大夫之妻一也雜記云外宗爲君夫人猶内</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='1944:1964'>宗是君之姑姉妺之女舅之女從母之女皆爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='1964:1984'>諸侯服斬爲夫人服期是二也此文外宗是諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='1984:2004'>侯外宗之婦也若姑之子婦從母之子婦其夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2004:2031'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-5b' );" name="028-5b" class="pb">[028-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2031:2051'>是君之外親爲君服斬其婦亦名外宗爲君服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2051:2071'>期是三也内宗有二者案周禮云内女之有爵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2071:2091'>謂其同姓之女悉是一也雜記云内宗者是君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2091:2111'>之五屬之内女是二也引喪大記曰外宗房中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2111:2122'>南靣者證外宗之義也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2122:2137'><span class='krp-note'>十/二</span>禫而飲醴酒食乾肉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2137:2158'>又期而大祥有醯醬者謂至大祥之節食醯醬則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2158:2178'>小祥食菜果之時但用鹽酪也若不能食者小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2178:2198'>祥食菜果之時得用醯醬也故喪大記云小祥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2198:2225'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-6a' );" name="028-6a" class="pb">[028-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2225:2244'>食菜果以醯醬中月而禫禫而飲醴酒又云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2244:2264'>食肉者先食乾肉喪大記云祥而食肉者異人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2264:2284'>之說故不同也　注先飲醴酒食乾肉者不忍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2284:2303'>發御厚味正義曰以醴酒味薄乾肉又澁所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2303:2324'>以先食之者以喪服除孝子不忍發𥘉御醇厚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2324:2336'>之味故飲醴酒食乾肉也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2336:2353'><span class='krp-note'>十/三</span>有事其縷無事其布曰緦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2353:2373'>有事其縷無事其布曰緦者以三月之喪治其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2373:2393'>麻縷其細如緦故云緦麻以朝服十五升抽去</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2393:2420'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-6b' );" name="028-6b" class="pb">[028-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2420:2440'>其半縷細而䟽也有事其縷事謂鍜治其布纑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2440:2460'>縷也無事其布謂織布旣成不鍜治其布以哀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2460:2466'>在外故也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2466:2485'><span class='krp-note'>十/四</span>冠衰升數及練以後除脫之差</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2485:2506'>斬衰三升者此明父母之喪𥘉死至練冠衰升</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2506:2526'>數之變并明練後除脫之差也受以成布六升</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2526:2546'>者以言三升四升五升之布其縷旣麤䟽未爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2546:2566'>成布也六升以下其縷漸細與吉布相參故稱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2566:2585'>成布也葛帶三重者謂男子也旣虞卒哭受</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2585:2612'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-7a' );" name="028-7a" class="pb">[028-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2612:2632'>服之節要中之帶以葛代麻帶又差小於前以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2632:2652'>五分去一唯有四分見在三重謂作四股糾之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2652:2672'>積而相重四股則三重未受服之前麻帶爲兩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2672:2692'>股相合也此直云葛帶三重則首絰雖葛不三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2692:2712'>重也猶兩股糾之也　期而小祥練冠縓縁者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2712:2732'>父没爲母與父同也至小祥又以卒哭後冠受</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2732:2752'>其衰而用練易其冠也又練爲中衣以縓爲領</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2752:2772'>縁也　又期而大祥素縞麻衣者謂二十五月</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2772:2792'>大祥祭此日除脫則首服素冠以縞紕之身著</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2792:2819'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-7b' );" name="028-7b" class="pb">[028-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2819:2839'>朝服而爲大祥之祭祭訖之後而哀情未除更</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2839:2859'>反服微凶之服首著縞冠以素紕之身著十五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='2859:2878'>升麻深衣未有采縁故云大祥素縞麻衣也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='2878:2898'>中月而禫者中間也大祥之後更間一月而爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='2898:2917'>禫祭二十五月大祥二十七月而禫禫而纎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='2917:2937'>者禫祭之時玄冠朝服禫祭旣訖而首著纎冠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='2937:2957'>身着素端黃裳以至吉祭　無所不佩者吉祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='2957:2976'>之時身㝷常吉服平常所服之物無不佩也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='2976:2994'><span class='krp-note'>十/五</span>鄭釋至親以期斷未盡經意</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='2994:3021'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-8a' );" name="028-8a" class="pb">[028-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3021:3041'>何以至期也曰至親以期斷注曰言三年之義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3041:3061'>如此則何以有降至於期也期者謂爲人後者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3061:3081'>父在爲母也言服之正雖在親皆期而除也正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3081:3101'>義曰鄭意以三年之䘮何以有降至於期者故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3101:3121'>云爲人後者爲夲生之父母及父在爲母期事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3121:3141'>故抑屈應降至九月十月何以必至於期以其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3141:3161'>夲至親不可降期以下故雖降屈猶至於期今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3161:3181'>檢㝷經意父母本應三年何以至期者但問其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3181:3201'>一期應除之義故答曰至親期斷是明一期可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3201:3228'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-8b' );" name="028-8b" class="pb">[028-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3228:3248'>除之節故禮期而練男子除絰婦人除帶下文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3248:3268'>云加隆故至三年是經意不據爲人後及父在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3268:3288'>爲母期鄭之此釋恐未盡經意但旣祖鄭學今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3288:3294'>因而釋之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3294:3309'><span class='krp-note'>十/六</span>三秊喪未知所由來</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3309:3329'>故三年之喪人道之至文者也夫是之謂至隆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3329:3349'>是百王之所同古今之所壹也未有知其所由</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3349:3369'>來者也注云言三年之喪喪禮之最盛也不知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3369:3389'>其所從來喻此三年之喪前丗行之乆矣正義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3389:3416'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-9a' );" name="028-9a" class="pb">[028-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3416:3436'>曰案易繫辭云古之葬者厚衣之以薪葬之中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3436:3456'>野不封不樹䘮期無數尚書云百姓如䘮考妣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3456:3476'>三載此云不知所由來者但上古云䘮期無數</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3476:3496'>謂無葬練祥之數其䘮父母之哀猶三年也故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3496:3516'>堯崩云如䘮考妣三載則知堯以前䘮考妣巳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3516:3536'>三年但不知定在何時其䘮服所起則黃帝堯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3536:3556'>舜之時雖有衣裳仍未有䘮服也但唐虞巳前</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3556:3576'>䘮服與吉服同皆以白布爲之故郊特牲云大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3576:3596'>古冠布齊則緇之若不齊則皆用白布也鄭注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3596:3623'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-9b' );" name="028-9b" class="pb">[028-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3623:3643'>䘮服其冠衰之異從三代以下由唐虞以上曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3643:3661'>大古吉㐫皆用白布則知三代吉㐫異也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3661:3676'><span class='krp-note'>十/八</span>深衣長衣中衣之別</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3676:3696'>案鄭目録云名曰深衣者以其記深衣之制也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3696:3716'>深衣連衣裳而純之以采者素純曰長衣有表</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3716:3736'>則謂之中衣大夫以上祭服之中衣用素詩云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3736:3756'>素衣朱襮玉藻曰以帛裏布非禮也士祭以朝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3756:3776'>服中衣以布明矣此於別録屬制度鄭云大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3776:3796'>以上祭服中衣用素者謂天子大夫以其四命</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3796:3824'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-10a' );" name="028-10a" class="pb">[028-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3824:3844'>與公之孤同爵弁自祭故中衣用素云士祭以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3844:3864'>朝服中衣以布者亦謂天子之士與諸侯大夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3864:3884'>同案少牢諸侯大夫祭以朝服故天子之士亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3884:3904'>祭以朝服朝服用布故中衣以布其諸侯之士</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='3904:3924'>自祭以玄端玄端則朝服之衣但其裳異耳中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='3924:3944'>衣亦用布也案詩云素衣朱襮晉人欲薦桓叔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='3944:3964'>桓叔大夫得用素衣者國人以國君之禮待之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='3964:3984'>故欲薦素衣也其長衣中衣及深衣其制度同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='3984:4004'>玉藻云長中繼揜尺若深衣則縁而已下云縁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='4004:4032'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-10b' );" name="028-10b" class="pb">[028-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='4032:4052'>廣寸半凡深衣皆用諸侯大夫士夕時所着之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4052:4072'>服故玉藻云朝玄端夕深衣庶人吉服亦深衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4072:4092'>皆著之在表也其中衣在朝服祭服䘮服之下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4092:4112'>知䘮服亦有中衣者檀弓云練衣黃裏注云練</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4112:4132'>中衣以黃爲内是也但䘮服中衣不得繼揜尺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4132:4152'>也故䘮服儀云帶縁各視其冠注云縁如深衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4152:4172'>之縁是䘮服中衣用深衣則深衣縁之以采故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4172:4192'>下云具父母大父母衣純以繢以青之屬也唯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4192:4212'>孤子深衣純以素但以縁而巳不與長衣同其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4212:4240'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-11a' );" name="028-11a" class="pb">[028-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4240:4260'>吉服中衣亦以采縁其諸侯得綃黼爲領丹朱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4260:4280'>爲縁郊特牲云綃黼丹朱中衣大夫之僣禮則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4280:4300'>知大夫士不用綃黼丹朱但用采純而已矣無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4300:4320'>文以明之其長衣以素縁知者若以采縁則與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4320:4340'>吉服中衣同故知以素縁也若以布縁則曰麻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4340:4360'>衣知用布縁者以其稱麻衣故知也其䘮服之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4360:4380'>中衣其純用布視冠布之麤細至葬可以用素</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4380:4400'>縁也練則用縓也其詩麻衣則與此別彼謂吉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4400:4420'>服之衣也所以此稱深衣者以餘服則上衣下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4420:4448'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-11b' );" name="028-11b" class="pb">[028-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4448:4469'>裳不相連此深衣衣裳相連𬒳體深䆳故謂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4469:4473'>深衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4473:4488'><span class='krp-note'>二/四</span>深衣應規矩繩權衡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4488:4508'>古者深衣蓋有制度以應規矩繩權衡短毋見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4508:4529'>膚長毋𬒳土續祍鉤邊要縫半下袼之髙下可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4529:4550'>以運肘𬒮之長短反詘之及肘注云言聖人制</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4550:4570'>事必有法度衣取蔽形爲汙辱也續猶屬也祍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='4570:4590'>在裳旁者也屬連之不殊裳前後也鉤讀如鳥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='4590:4612'>啄必鉤之鉤鉤邊若今曲𥚑也續或爲𥙿三分</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='4612:4640'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-12a' );" name="028-12a" class="pb">[028-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='4640:4660'>要中減一以益下下宜寛也要或爲優肘不能</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='4660:4682'>不岀入袼衣𬒮當掖之縫也𬒮屬幅於衣詘而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4682:4703'>至肘當臂中爲節臂骨上下各尺二寸則𬒮肘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4703:4714'>以前尺二寸肘或爲腕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4714:4723'><span class='krp-note'>二/五</span>同上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4723:4744'>𬒮圜以應規曲袷如矩以應方負繩及踝以應</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4744:4764'>直下齊如權衡以應平注云圜謂胡下也祫交</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4764:4784'>領也古者方領如今小兒衣領繩謂裻與後幅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4784:4796'>相當之縫也踝踉也齊緝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4796:4824'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-12b' );" name="028-12b" class="pb">[028-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4824:4839'><span class='krp-note'>二/六</span>完且弗費善衣之次</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4839:4859'>完且弗費善衣之次也注云完且弗費言可苦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4859:4879'>衣而易有也深衣者用十五升布鍜濯灰治純</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='4879:4899'>之以采善衣朝祭之服也自士以上深衣爲之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='4899:4910'>次庶人吉服深衣而巳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='4910:4921'><span class='krp-note'>二/七</span>純縁之飾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='4921:4941'>具父母大父母衣純以繢具父母衣純以青如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='4941:4962'>孤子衣純以素純𬒮縁純邊廣各寸半注云尊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='4962:4982'>者存以多飾爲孝繢畫文也三十巳下無父稱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='4982:5010'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-13a' );" name="028-13a" class="pb">[028-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='5010:5031'>孤純謂縁之也縁𬒮謂其口也縁緆也縁邊衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='5031:5051'>裳之側廣各寸半則表裏共三寸矣唯祫廣二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='5051:5086'>寸<span class='krp-note'>陸云鄭注旣夕禮飾衣領𬒮口曰純/裳邊側曰綼下曰緆以豉反又音錫</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5086:5098'><span class='krp-note'>二/八</span>釋續衽鈎邉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='5098:5118'>正義曰衽當旁者凡深衣之裳十二幅皆寛頭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='5118:5138'>在下狹頭在上皆似小要之衽是前後左右皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='5138:5158'>有祍也今云祍當旁者所續之祍當身之一旁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='5158:5178'>非爲餘祍悉當旁也云屬連之不殊裳前後也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5178:5198'>若其䘮服其裳前三幅後四幅各自爲之不相</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='5198:5226'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-13b' );" name="028-13b" class="pb">[028-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='5226:5246'>連也今深衣裳一旁則連之相著一旁則有曲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='5246:5267'>𥚑掩之與相連無異故云屬連之不殊裳前後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='5267:5287'>也云鉤讀如鳥喙必鉤之鉤者案援神契云象</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='5287:5307'>鼻必卷長鳥喙必鉤鄭據此讀之也云若今曲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='5307:5329'>𥚑也鄭以後漢之時裳有曲𥚑故以續祍鉤邊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='5329:5350'>似漢時曲𥚑今時朱衣朝服從後漢明帝所爲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='5350:5372'>則鄭云今曲𥚑者是今朝服之曲𥚑也其衣之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='5372:5381'>衽巳於玉藻釋之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='5381:5398'><span class='krp-note'>二/九</span>要縫半下畔當七尺二寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='5398:5426'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-14a' );" name="028-14a" class="pb">[028-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='5426:5446'>要縫謂要中之縫尺寸闊狹半下畔之闊下畔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='5446:5463'>一丈四尺四寸則要縫半之七尺二寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='5463:5479'><span class='krp-note'>三/十</span>三分要中減一以益下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='5479:5499'>正義曰此據裳之一幅分爲二幅凡布廣二尺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='5499:5519'>二寸四寸爲縫一尺八寸在三分之一分爲六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='5519:5539'>寸減此六寸以益於下是下二幅有二尺四寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='5539:5559'>上二幅有一尺二寸故云三分要中減一以益</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='5559:5572'>下下容舉足而行故宜寛也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='5572:5587'><span class='krp-note'>三/一</span>袼之髙下可以運肘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='5587:5615'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-14b' );" name="028-14b" class="pb">[028-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='5615:5636'>袼之髙下可以運肘　袼謂當臂之處𬒮中髙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='5636:5657'>下宜寛大可以運動其肘𬒮二尺二寸肘尺二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='5657:5678'>寸是容運肘也　𬒮之長短反詘之及肘者袂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='5678:5698'>長二尺二寸并縁寸半爲二尺三寸半除去其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='5698:5718'>縫之所殺各一寸餘有二尺一寸半在從肩至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='5718:5738'>手二尺四寸今二尺一寸半之袂得反詘及肘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='5738:5759'>者以𬒮屬於衣幅闊二尺二寸身脊至肩但尺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='5759:5779'>一寸也從肩覆臂又尺一寸是衣幅之畔覆臂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='5779:5800'>將盡今又屬𬒮於衣又二尺一寸半故反詘其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='5800:5828'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-15a' );" name="028-15a" class="pb">[028-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='5828:5837'>𬒮得及於肘也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='5837:5854'><span class='krp-note'>三/二</span>深衣帶下於朝祭服之帶</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='5854:5874'>當無骨者帶若當骨則緩急難中故當無骨之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='5874:5894'>處此深衣帶下於朝祭服之帶也朝祭之帶則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='5894:5914'>近上故玉藻云三分帶下紳居二焉是自帶以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='5914:5922'>下四尺五寸也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='5922:5935'><span class='krp-note'>三/三</span>方領似漢擁咽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='5935:5955'>古者方領　正義曰鄭以漢時領皆嚮下交垂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='5955:5975'>故云古者方領似今擁咽故云若今小兒衣領</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='5975:6003'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-15b' );" name="028-15b" class="pb">[028-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='6003:6010'>但方折之也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='6010:6028'><span class='krp-note'>三/四</span>負繩抱方以直其政方其義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='6028:6048'>負繩抱方者以直其政方其義也負繩背之縫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='6048:6068'>也抱方領之方也以直其政解負繩以方其義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='6068:6088'>解抱方也言欲使人直其政教欲使政教直方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='6088:6099'>其義欲使義事方正也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='6099:6117'><span class='krp-note'>三/五</span>直方地之性言坤二得中氣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='6117:6137'>案鄭注坤之六二云直也方也地之性此爻得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='6137:6157'>中氣而在地上自然之性廣生萬物故生動直</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='6157:6185'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-16a' );" name="028-16a" class="pb">[028-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='6185:6190'>而且方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='6190:6208'><span class='krp-note'>三/六</span>深衣士服之次庻人之吉服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='6208:6228'>䘮服麻衣雖似深衣之制不必鍛濯灰治以其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='6228:6248'>雜凶故也云自士以上深衣爲之次者案玉藻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='6248:6268'>諸侯夕深衣祭牢肉又大夫士朝玄端夕深衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='6268:6288'>是深衣爲朝祭之次服也云庶人吉服深衣者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='6288:6308'>深衣是諸侯之下自深衣以後更無餘服故知</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='6308:6328'>是庶人之吉服䘮服有衰裳包貴賤上下無差</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='6328:6340'>亦明庶人吉服乃深衣也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='6340:6368'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-16b' );" name="028-16b" class="pb">[028-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='6368:6382'><span class='krp-note'>三/七</span>縁純表裏共三寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='6382:6404'>純𬒮縁純邊廣各寸半者純𬒮者純縁也謂純</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='6404:6426'>其𬒮縁則𬒮口也又云縁讀爲緆謂深衣之下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='6426:6446'>純也純邊者謂深衣之旁側也廣各寸半者言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='6446:6467'>純𬒮口及裳下之緆井純旁邊其廣各寸半言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='6467:6475'>表裏合爲三寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='6475:6488'><span class='krp-note'>三/八</span>再釋純縁綼緆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='6488:6510'>純𬒮則是縁其𬒮口也非是口外更有縁也故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='6510:6530'>分明言之云縁緆也解經縁字讀爲緆謂深衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='6530:6558'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-17a' );" name="028-17a" class="pb">[028-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='6558:6578'>下畔也故旣夕禮云明衣縓綼緆鄭注云在幅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='6578:6598'>曰綼在下曰緆今經云此緆則深衣之下縁也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='6598:6618'>云縁邊衣裳之側解經純邊也深衣外衿之邊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='6618:6639'>有縁也裳雖前後相連然外邊曲𥚑揜處其側</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='6639:6645'>亦有縁也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='6645:6656'>禮記要義卷第二十九</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='6656:6684'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0055', 'SBCK', '028-17b' );" name="028-17b" class="pb">[028-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
